```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# a sequence of numbers from 1 to 10 with increment 2
(seq_vec <- seq(from = 1, to = 10, by = 2))
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 1 3 5 7 9
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(seq_vec)
