:::

::: {.column width="50%"}

::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
str(x_lst)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
List of 3
 $ idx: int [1:3] 1 2 3
 $    : chr "a"
 $    : logi [1:2] TRUE FALSE
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
names(x_lst)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "idx" ""    ""   
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
length(x_lst)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 3
```
:::
:::

